---
import WidgetLayout from '../../layouts/WidgetLayout.astro';
---
<WidgetLayout title="Spinner">
  <h1>Spinner</h1>
  <p>Animated loading indicator using braille frames.</p>

  <h2>Preview</h2>
  <pre class="ascii-mockup">Syncing... ⠋  →  ⠙  →  ⠹  →  ⠸  →  ...</pre>

  <h2>Braille frames</h2>
  <p>Default frame sequence: <code>⠋⠙⠹⠸⠼⠴⠦⠧⠇⠏</code></p>

  <h2>Accessible mode</h2>
  <p><code>Syncing...</code> (ARIA <code>role="status"</code>, <code>aria-live="polite"</code> &mdash; screen reader announces once, no animation)</p>

  <h2>Props</h2>
  <table>
    <thead><tr><th>Prop</th><th>Type</th><th>Notes</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>label</td><td>string?</td><td></td></tr>
      <tr><td>frames</td><td>string[]?</td><td>default braille: <code>⠋⠙⠹⠸⠼⠴⠦⠧⠇⠏</code></td></tr>
      <tr><td>interval</td><td>number?</td><td>ms, default 80</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2>Interactive demo</h2>
  <div class="demo-placeholder">Interactive demo coming soon</div>
</WidgetLayout>
